></font></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=60 valign=top bgcolor="#99CCFF" style='width:45.0pt;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;background:#99CCFF;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'>\r\n  <p class=MsoPlainText><font size=2 face="Courier New"><span style='font-size:10.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></font></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=252 valign=top bgcolor="#99CCFF" style='width:189.0pt;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;background:#99CCFF;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'>\r\n  <p class=MsoPlainText><font size=2 face="Courier New"><span style='font-size:10.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=120 valign=top bgcolor="#99CCFF" style='width:1.25in;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;background:#99CCFF;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'>\r\n  <p class=MsoPlainText><font size=2 face="Courier New"><span style='font-size:10.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></font></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr>\r\n  <td width=119 valign=top bgcolor="#99CCFF" style='width:89.6pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-top:none;background:#99CCFF;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'>\r\n  <p class=MsoPlainText><font size=2 face="Courier New"><span style='font-size:10.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></font></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n\r\n  <td width=60 valign=top bgcolor="#99CCFF" style='width:45.0pt;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;background:#99CCFF;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'>\r\n  <p class=MsoPlainText><font size=2 face="Courier New"><span style='font-size:10.0pt'>Flash Size<o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=252 valign=top bgcolor="#99CCFF" style='width:189.0pt;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;background:#99CCFF;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'>\r\n  <p class=MsoPlainText><font size=2 face="Courier New"><span style='font-size:10.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></font></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=120 valign=top bgcolor="#99CCFF" style='width:1.25in;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;background:#99CCFF;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'>\r\n  <p class=MsoPlainText><font size=2 face="Courier New"><span style='font-size:10.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n</table>\r\n<p />\r\n<h4><a name="Flashing_X_Loader_and_U_Boot"></a> Flashing X-Loader and U-Boot </h4> <ul>\r\n<li> Load u-boot.out (ELF file format) using CCS.\r\n</li> <li> Flash X-Loader using U-Boot (Send the attached X-Loader with Kermit).\r\n</li></ul> \r\n<blockquote><pre>\r\n\r\nloadb 0x80200000 115200;\r\nonenand unlock 0 0;onenand unlock 1 0;onenand unlock 2 0;onenand unlock 3 0;onenand erase block 0-3;\r\nonenand write 80200000 0 2000;\r\n</pre></blockquote> <ul>\r\n<li> Flash U-Boot using U-Boot (Send the attached U-Boot with Kermit).\r\n</li></ul> \r\n<blockquote><pre>\r\nloadb 0x80300000 115200\r\nonenand unlock 4 0;onenand unlock 5 0;onenand erase block 4-5;\r\nonenand write 80300000 80000 40000;\r\n</pre></blockquote>  <ul>\r\n<li> Close CCS and remove board power.\r\n</li> <li> Remove EMU0 short.\r\n</li> <li> Power the board and observe U-Boot prompt.\r\n\r\n</li></ul> \r\n<p />\r\n<h4><a name="Flashing_Kernel_and_File_System"></a> Flashing Kernel and File System </h4>\r\nHere are the tested ONENAND commands and addresses to flash kernel and ramdisk image. <ul>\r\n<li> Flash the Kernel (Send the attached uImage with Kermit).\r\n</li></ul> \r\n<blockquote><pre>\r\nloadb 0x80300000 115200;\r\nonenand unlock 7 0;onenand unlock 8 0;onenand unlock 9 0;onenand unlock 10 0;\r\nonenand unlock 11 0;onenand unlock 12 0;onenand unlock 13 0;onenand unlock 14 0;\r\nonenand unlock 15 0;onenand unlock 16 0;onenand unlock 17 0;onenand unlock 18 0;\r\nonenand unlock 19 0;onenand unlock 20 0;onenand unlock 21 0;onenand unlock 22 0;\r\nonenand erase block 7-22;onenand write 80300000 e0000 1D0000;\r\n</pre></blockquote>\r\n<h5><a name="Use_a_RAMDISK_initialized_by_the"></a> Use a RAMDISK initialized by the ONENAND </h5> <ul>\r\n\r\n<li> Flash the RAMDISK file system (Send the attached ramdisk_ext2.gz with Kermit.)\r\n</li></ul> \r\n<blockquote><pre>\r\nloadb 0x81600000 115200;\r\nonenand unlock 23 0;onenand unlock 24 0;onenand unlock 25 0;onenand unlock 26 0;\r\nonenand unlock 27 0;onenand unlock 28 0;onenand unlock 29 0;onenand unlock 30 0;\r\nonenand unlock 31 0;onenand unlock 32 0;onenand unlock 33 0;onenand unlock 34 0;\r\nonenand unlock 35 0;onenand unlock 36 0;onenand unlock 37 0;onenand unlock 38 0;\r\nonenand unlock 39 0;onenand unlock 40 0;onenand unlock 41 0;onenand unlock 42 0;\r\nonenand unlock 43 0;onenand unlock 44 0;onenand unlock 45 0;onenand unlock 46 0;\r\nonenand unlock 47 0;onenand unlock 48 0;\r\nonenand erase block 23-48;onenand write 81600000 2E0000 300000;\r\n</pre></blockquote> <ul>\r\n<li> Configure U-Boot to load the kernel and file system.\r\n</li></ul> \r\n<blockquote><pre>\r\nsetenv bootargs 'console=tty0 console=ttyS0,115200n8 ramdisk_size=3072 root=/dev/ram0 rw rootfstype=ext2 initrd=0x81600000,3M';\r\nsetenv bootcmd 'onenand read 0x80300000 0xe0000 0x1d0000; run bootcmd_1;';\r\nsetenv bootcmd_1 'onenand read 0x81600000 0x2e0000 0x300000; run bootcmd_2;';\r\nsetenv bootcmd_2 'bootm 0x80300000';\r\nsetenv bootdelay 3;\r\nsaveenv\r\n</pre></blockquote>\r\n<h5><a name="Use_a_file_system_on_an_MMC_card"></a> Use a file system on an MMC card </h5>\r\n<blockquote><pre>\r\n\r\nsetenv bootargs 'console=tty0 console=ttyS0,115200n8 root=/dev/mmcblk0p1 rw rootdelay=1';\r\nsetenv bootcmd 'onenand read 0x80300000 0xe0000 0x1d0000; run bootcmd_1;';\r\nsetenv bootcmd_1 'bootm 0x80300000';\r\nsetenv bootdelay 3;\r\nsaveenv\r\n</pre></blockquote></div>	en-us	blog.hangerhead.com	2008-02-05 10:37:36.024	\N
